short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The best chrome startpage for developers.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ever felt that Chrome's default start page was just a bit too boring for you?   Look no further developers!   DevStart is the perfect start page for developers.   It is probably the most customisable start page for Chrome with developer-themed settings and customisability in almost every place imaginable.   

Features:
- Quick links
- Table of links
- Weather 
- Greetings
and more

Documentation for the extension is available at the extension's website (https://devstart.jtlr.me).  Still need help? We're happy to help you.   Shoot us an email or ask for support on Chrome Web Store.
